# DynamicNFC Cursor Rules (Entrypoint)
# Last updated: 2026-04-23
#
# This file is intentionally short.
# Source rules live in `.cursor/rules/*.mdc`.
#
# Rule loading order:
# 1) `.cursor/rules/00-core.mdc`
# 2) Other `.mdc` files by filename order
#
# Conflict policy:
# - Scoped rule beats generic rule.
# - If docs conflict with real code, verify real code first.
# - Never auto-edit rule files unless user explicitly asks.
